  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Food Sec for T&apos;boli families Sarangani Phil&apos;s.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Food insecurity describes the continual hunger periods and malnutrition, most especially among the children, of the 45 families of the T&apos;boli tribe in Sitio Datal Basak, Sarangani Province.  SIBAT in partnership with CLANS (Center for Lumad Advocacy &amp; Services) would like to address the chronic food insecurity of the T&apos;boli tribe by helping farmers develop their upland farms convert into organic farms - by providing farm tools, inputs and trainings in upland organic food production.</narrative>
  </description>
